      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>When you counter a spell, you can claim some of its thaumaturgic energies to regain your own cast spells.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Ability to cast spells</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you successfully counter an opponent’s spell, such as with <em>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.KQ4vSfG9tq8EJxir]{dispel magic}</em>, you can attempt a caster level check with a DC equal to the 10 + the countered spell’s level. On a success, regain a used spell slot equal to half the level of the spell countered in this way (minimum 1).</p>"
